ACCOUNT_DELETION_CONFIRM: Are you sure you want to permanently delete your account for this game?
ACCOUNT_DELETION_DETAIL:
These steps happen immediately: 
You are logged out of the game. 
Your game data is deleted from your device. 
Your game data is disconnected from all associated services. 

These steps can take up to 30 days to complete: 
Your game progress and in-game purchases are deleted from your account. 
All other data associated with your game account is deleted - including Sign in with Apple.

After submitting the Delete Account request, we strongly recommend that you do the following:
Cancel any subscriptions for the game. (Open the Settings app, tap your name, tap Subscriptions, and then remove the subscription from the list.) 
Uninstall the game from your device to ensure that no new game accounts or game data is created.
ACCOUNT_DELETION_DETAIL_GOOGLE:
These steps happen immediately: 
You are logged out of the game. 
Your game data is deleted from your device. 
Your game data is disconnected from all associated services. 

These steps can take up to 30 days to complete: 
Your game progress and in-game purchases are deleted from your account. 
All other data associated with your game account is deleted.

After submitting the Delete Account request, we strongly recommend that you do the following:
Cancel any subscriptions for the game. (Open the Settings app, tap your name, tap Subscriptions, and then remove the subscription from the list.) 
Uninstall the game from your device to ensure that no new game accounts or game data is created.
ACCOUNT_DELETION_LEARN_MORE:
Deleting your account is permanent and cannot be undone or reversed.

Tap NEXT to learn more about the Delete Account Process.
ACCOUNT_DELETION_TYPE_TO_CONFIRM: Please enter the numbers displayed on the screen.

COLL_POWERUP_WEBBY: Join Webby's Quacky Patch Doll and friends for a tea party!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGARIEL: Triton, Max, and Scuttle celebrate Ariel's wedding with heart-eyed Blitz emojis and a Rainbow Star!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGCINDERELLA: Cinderella and Prince Charming have a timeless moment with Jaq and Gus, and live happily ever after!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGGISELLE: Queen Narissa pushes Giselle down a well to a place where there are no happily ever afters!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGJASMINE: "I choose you, Aladdin." Jasmine and Aladdin enjoy a wonderful celebration surrounded by fireworks!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGMAXIMUS: Maximus is in full swing as he chases Rapunzel and Flynn's wedding ring!
COLL_POWERUP_WEDDINGMULAN: Celebration Mulan and Li Shang enjoy each other's company under the beautiful plum blossom tree!
COLL_POWERUP_WENDY: The Darlings fly with Peter Pan and Tink to Neverland! Follow the second star to the right!
COLL_POWERUP_WEREWOLFGOOFY: Werewolf Goofy befriends an adorable wolf in the daytime, and together they howl at the moon at night!
COLL_POWERUP_WHITERABBIT: For a short time, each match adds +1 second to the clock!
COLL_POWERUP_WICKET: Wicket and his Ewok friends hold off the Empire's AT-ST advance with their clever traps!
COLL_POWERUP_WINIFRED: Resurrects your most recently used powerups from the grave!
COLL_POWERUP_WINTERAURORA: Aurora and Prince Phillip dance beneath the northern lights, enchanting a row for bonus score!
COLL_POWERUP_WINTERDAISY: Winter Daisy puts the finishing touches on a perfect snowman... until Donald crashes into the scene!
COLL_POWERUP_WINTERPETE: Winter Pete and Spring Flute Mickey face off! Will the board be covered in icy winter or flowery spring?
COLL_POWERUP_WINTERSNOWWHITE: Winter Snow White and the dwarfs enjoy the snowy weather with a sleigh ride together!
COLL_POWERUP_WINTERTIMEPOCAHONTAS: Wintertime Pocahontas shows Meeko that there's no reason to fear sledding down a fun snowy slope!
COLL_POWERUP_WITCHMINNIE: Boo! Witch Minnie brews potions to conjure all kinds of magic!
COLL_POWERUP_WOODY: Tap the board to round up emojis with Woody's lasso!
COLL_POWERUP_WOODYSROUNDUPALIEN: Woody's Roundup Alien uses the powerups of Woody's whole gang from his famous television show!
COLL_POWERUP_WORLDOFCOLORMICKEY: Mickey brings the Wonderful World of Color to life with a spectacular rainbow water show!
COLL_POWERUP_YENSID: Yen Sid creates a tidal wave and washes away the entire board!
COLL_POWERUP_YESSS: Clear emojis fast to earn hearts! If you like it, better put a heart on it!
COLL_POWERUP_YODA: "Do or do not. There is no try." Yoda teaches Luke an important lesson as they free the X-wing!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGANAKIN: Tap left or right to avoid obstacles, clearing emojis with Ani's thrusters! Now this is pod racing!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGANNA: "Do you want to build a snowman?" Bring Olaf to life by dragging snowballs to the correct position!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGJUDY: "I can make the world a better place!" Young Judy Hopp's determination powers her impressive leap over the board!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGMERIDA: Tap on a path to guide Young Merida to her lost arrow!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGMIM: Young Mim charms the emojis to become heart-eyed, but they shouldn't get too comfortable...
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGTIANA: "I think it's done, Daddy!" Young Tiana gives her Dad a taste of her home-cooked Gumbo!
COLL_POWERUP_YOUNGWINIFRED: Young Winifred and her sisters reveal their striking powers with a magical spell that shocks the emojis!
COLL_POWERUP_YZMA: Tap a lever to create a potion or drop Yzma, transforming or clearing emojis!
COLL_POWERUP_ZAZU: Tap a bone pile to help Zazu find Simba and Nala!
COLL_POWERUP_ZERO: Zero lights the way to deliver terrifying presents from Halloween Town!
COLL_POWERUP_ZEUS: I need more thunderbolts! Match fast to zap the board!
COLL_POWERUP_ZUMMIGUMMI: Zummi Gummi uses a powerful spell from the Great Book of Gummi and casts it over the board!
COLL_POWERUP_ZURG: "Destroy Buzz Lightyear!" Zurg blasts Buzz with his ion blaster, creating powerups on the board.
